Class NElementFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • spas.nhandling.nelements.NElementFactory

  • public class NElementFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory-class for creating different NElements. Mostly so that the only thing required to do is call this one method instead of calling each and every NElement's own constructor.
